flowchart TD
    A[Initialize OxfordPetDataset] --> B[Store root split image_size val_ratio seed augment]
    B --> C[Set dataset paths]
    C --> D[Validate required paths exist]

    D --> E[Build samples]
    E --> F{Requested split?}

    F -->|test| G[Read IDs from test.txt]
    G --> H[Create sample pairs image path and mask path]
    H --> I[Dataset ready]

    F -->|trainval| J[Read IDs from trainval.txt]
    J --> K[Create sample pairs image path and mask path]
    K --> I

    F -->|train or val| L[Read IDs from trainval.txt]
    L --> M[Deterministically shuffle IDs]
    M --> N[Split IDs into train and val]
    N --> O{train or val?}
    O -->|train| P[Create train sample pairs]
    O -->|val| Q[Create val sample pairs]
    P --> I
    Q --> I

    I --> R[__getitem__ called]
    R --> S[Load RGB image]
    S --> T[Load trimap mask]
    T --> U[Convert trimap to binary mask]
    U --> V[Apply joint transforms to image and mask]
    V --> W[Convert image to tensor]
    W --> X[Normalize image tensor]
    X --> Y[Convert mask to tensor]
    Y --> Z[Return image tensor and mask tensor]